## Project Summary
Fractal is an AI-powered idea synthesis tool that maps relationships between concepts and presents them as an expandable visual network. It is not a search engine — it shows structural forces, tensions, and emergent patterns shaping a big question.

**Current Status:** Demo built with hardcoded data for one query. Basic node/edge visual rendering works. Next step is connecting a live LLM backend.

