## LLM Decision Summary

| Stage | Solution | Cost |
|---|---|---|
| Building now | Ollama locally | Free |
| Demo / mockup | Groq free tier | Free |
| Early growth | Groq paid | Low |
| 100k+ users | Fine-tuned Llama 3, self-hosted | Flat rate, much cheaper |
| Never | Train from scratch | Not worth it at any stage |

